{"title":"C","uid":"30d0e8b4fec8f0e7fdc112e7d2774cdb","slug":"C/C","date":"2021-11-02T03:39:04.000Z","updated":"2022-06-11T15:29:41.915Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/C/C.json","keywords":null,"cover":"/img/C.jpeg","content":"<h2 id=\"数组指针-amp-指针数组\"><a href=\"#数组指针-amp-指针数组\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"数组指针&amp;指针数组\"></a>数组指针&amp;指针数组</h2><p><strong>1. 函数指针 &amp; 指针函数</strong></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-cpp\" data-language=\"cpp\"><code class=\"language-cpp\"><span class=\"token comment\">/*** 函数指针 ***/</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token operator\">*</span>fun<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">float</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// 一个指针，指向参数float、返回值void的函数</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">//函数地址的获取，可以直接函数名，也可以加取地址符&amp;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">/*** 指针函数 ***/</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">int</span><span class=\"token operator\">*</span> <span class=\"token function\">fun</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">float</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> \n<span class=\"token comment\">//一个函数，参数float、返回值为int*</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">/**函数指针数组**/</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token operator\">*</span>s<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">5</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">int</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">//s[5]说明是数组，数组的内容是void (*)(int)类型的函数指针</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<p><strong>2. 数组指针 &amp; 指针数组</strong></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-cpp\" data-language=\"cpp\"><code class=\"language-cpp\"><span class=\"token keyword\">int</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token operator\">*</span>a<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">10</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>  \n<span class=\"token comment\">//一个指针，指向int[10]数组; 对应二级指针级别  int **a、int a[][]</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">int</span> <span class=\"token operator\">*</span>a<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">10</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">//一个数组，含10个int*变量</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<p><strong>3. 相关计算</strong></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-cpp\" data-language=\"cpp\"><code class=\"language-cpp\"><span class=\"token keyword\">int</span> c<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">4</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">5</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token operator\">*</span>p<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">5</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\np <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> c<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\np<span class=\"token operator\">+</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span>  <span class=\"token comment\">//指向第一行地址</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">*</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>p<span class=\"token operator\">+</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> p<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>  <span class=\"token comment\">//第1行首地址</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">*</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>p<span class=\"token operator\">+</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token operator\">+</span><span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> p<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token operator\">+</span><span class=\"token number\">2</span>  <span class=\"token comment\">//第1行第2列地址</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">*</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>p<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token operator\">+</span><span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>  <span class=\"token comment\">//第1行第2列元素</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"运算符优先级\"><a href=\"#运算符优先级\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"运算符优先级\"></a>运算符优先级</h2><blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><ul>\n<li><p>一元前缀、三元、赋值运算符<strong>从右向左</strong>结合</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>**后置a++**等价于三步：tmp = a;  ++a; return tmp;</p>\n<p>  因为a++返回的是右值(rvalue)，不能对<strong>右值</strong>（将结束生命周期的对象）自增，故++(a++)报错</p>\n</li>\n</ul></blockquote>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>优先级</th>\n<th>类型</th>\n<th>运算符</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody><tr>\n<td>0</td>\n<td>一元后缀运算符</td>\n<td>()  []  ++  –  -&gt;  .</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>1</td>\n<td>一元前缀运算符</td>\n<td>++  –   +  -  !  * &amp; (type) sizeof</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>2</td>\n<td>算术运算符</td>\n<td>*  /  %   <code>&gt;</code>  ±</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>3</td>\n<td>位运算符</td>\n<td>&gt;&gt;  &lt;&lt;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>4</td>\n<td>关系运算符</td>\n<td>&gt;=  &gt;  &lt;  &lt;=  <code>&gt;</code>  ==  !=</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>5</td>\n<td>位逻辑运算符</td>\n<td>&amp;  <code>&gt;</code>  ^  <code>&gt;</code>   |</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>6</td>\n<td>逻辑运算符</td>\n<td>&amp;&amp; <code>&gt;</code> ||</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>7</td>\n<td>三元运算符</td>\n<td>? :</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>8</td>\n<td>赋值运算符</td>\n<td>=  +=  -=  *=  /=  %=  …</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>9</td>\n<td>逗号运算符</td>\n<td>,</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<h2 id=\"引用与指针\"><a href=\"#引用与指针\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"引用与指针\"></a>引用与指针</h2><ol>\n<li>内存方面：指针是变量，存放地址；引用是变量的别名，不占内存，底层实现为指针</li>\n<li>空值：指针可为空；引用必须定义时初始化为特定对象</li>\n<li>指针可改变；引用不能改变引用对象</li>\n<li>sizeof和自增(++)意义不同</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"重载-overload-、覆盖-override-、隐藏-hide-的区别\"><a href=\"#重载-overload-、覆盖-override-、隐藏-hide-的区别\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"重载(overload)、覆盖(override)、隐藏(hide)的区别\"></a>重载(overload)、覆盖(override)、隐藏(hide)的区别</h2><p><strong>重载</strong>是指<strong>同一个类</strong>中函数同名但参数不同，根据参数来区分调用。</p>\n<p><strong>覆盖</strong>是指派生类中对基类中的<strong>虚函数<code>(virtual)</code>重新实现</strong>。即函数名和参数都一样，但实现体不一样。</p>\n<p><strong>隐藏</strong>是指派生类中的函数把基类中<strong>同名函数屏蔽</strong>了。触发的结果取决于指针类型：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>若本身是基类指针(不管指向基类/派生类)则仍然调用基类成员;</li>\n<li>若本身是派生类指针，则隐藏基类成员，只会调用派生类成员。</li>\n<li><strong>如果调用的函数是实函数，则看指针的定义；如果调用的函数是虚函数，则看指针的指向（赋值）</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p> 在定义派生类的对象时，先调用父类的构造函数，在调用成员的构造函数，最后调用派生类的构造函数。 </p>\n<p>  引用是除指针外另一个可以产生多态效果的手段。这意味着，一个基类的引用可以指向它的派生类实例 </p>\n<p> 含有纯虚函数的类是抽象类，对于继承这样的类的类（派生类）来说，如果派生类实现了基类的纯虚函数，则派生类可以实例化。若派生类没有实现该纯虚函数，则该派生类也是抽象类，即不能实例化。</p>\n<p> <strong>抽象类有一下几个特点：</strong></p>\n<p> （1）抽象类只能用作其他类的基类，不能建立抽象类对象。</p>\n<p> （2）抽象类不能用作参数类型、函数返回类型或显式转换的类型。</p>\n<p> （3）可以定义指向抽象类的指针和引用，此指针可以指向它的派生类，进而实现多态性。</p></blockquote>\n<p><img src=\"https://uploadfiles.nowcoder.com/images/20200617/561761500_1592369570620_87EE87B02DD1E04C7A958617C618CFC4\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://uploadfiles.nowcoder.com/images/20210322/274519953_1616401735505/2DDE9FC0B97FEA06451FF02B48B0690B\"></p>\n","text":"数组指针&amp;指针数组1. 函数指针 &amp; 指针函数 /*** 函数指针 ***/ void (*fun)(float) // 一个指针，指向参数float、返回值void的函数 //函数地址的获取，可以直接函数名，也可以加取地址符&amp; /*** 指针函数 ***...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"1.6k","symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"C","slug":"C","count":3,"path":"api/categories/C.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"C"